description: Everyone in Austin knows that Pok-e-Jo’s is the place to go for tasty Texas BBQ. These guys are the smokey pros. After unveiling their first restaurant back in 1979, it was clear to owners Porky, Joe, and Doug that their mission to offer better BBQ to the people of Austin was a massive success. Now, not only are there 5 busy locations throughout Bat City, but you can also find their UT Orange truck buckin’ its way through town and ‘bringing the Q to you'!Come delight in your Pok-e favorites and fork into plump pulled pork or juicy, tender beef brisket - and don’t forget that tangy sauce. Order up a side of Texas pride in the form of velvety Potato Salad, savory Green Bean Casserole, and lusciously rich creamed corn, just to name a few.You’ll be fixin’ to queue up at this Texan truck for this delicious Q.
name: Pok-e-Jo's BBQ Truck
